data.description: Check out this restored beauty on 1.79 acres!! 3 beds, 2 full baths, living area with woodburning fireplace and french doors to covered back patio overlooking tree shaded property complete with a pond! Kitchen with nice cabinets, granite counters and stainless appliances. Master with barndoor entrance to master bath featuring double sinks, granite counters and a really pretty tub/shower combo AND a great-sized walk-in closet. Inside utility room, storage closets, double garage and ready for YOU! Call your favorite agent today for your private tour!
